1124.name: CuAl8Ni6
1124.Applications: Desalting installations, CuNiAl ship propellers, cladding against corrosion, cladding against wear, gliding surfaces, shipbuilding, pump building, shafts, guide grooves, tube systems etc
1124.Suitable_For: CuNiAl, CuAlNi, aluminum bronze, ship propellers, 2.0923, UNS C63000, C630AlBz, Joint welds or building up of aluminum bronze. Cladding (steel) components undergoing metal to metal wear under high pressure. Especially suited for marine environments. The addition of nickel improves corrosion resistance in heat and rough seawater.
